#

Tomato and Hummus Toast

5 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

WheatSesame

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

Quick MealHealthy SnackEasy Recipe

Description

A refreshing and healthy toast topped with creamy hummus and fresh tomatoes, perfect for a quick snack or light meal.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • hummus: 1/2 cup
  • tomatoes: 1 cup, diced
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • balsamic glaze: 1 tablespoon (optional)
